code: @Override public boolean equals(Object o) {     if (this == o) {         return true.     }     if (o == null || this.getClass() != o.getClass()) {         return false.     }     ApplicationResourcePrivileges that = (ApplicationResourcePrivileges) o.     return application.equals(that.application) && privileges.equals(that.privileges) && resources.equals(that.resources). }
@Override public int hashCode() {     return Objects.hash(application, privileges, resources). }
